          h2.ms-heading-2.ms-mb-6 4. Data Security
          p.ms-text-base.ms-leading-relaxed.ms-mb-4
            | We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your
            | personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or
            | destruction. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic
            | storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
          p.ms-text-base.ms-leading-relaxed.ms-mb-4
            | We use industry-standard security measures, including:
          ul.ms-list-disc.ms-list-inside.ms-space-y-2.ms-mb-6.ms-ml-4
            li Encryption of data in transit using SSL/TLS
            li Secure data storage with access controls
            li Regular security assessments and updates
            li Employee training on data protection

